name: Gallerie_Decor_Natural_Spa_Bamboo_Wall_Cabinet
reviews: Small but nice, fits well in a small bathroom

We got rid of the portable stack rack and upgraded for hidden cabinet items. Stores 4 rolls, hand towels and mini travel items for house guests where/when mirrored cabinets won't do. "This is a must have"

When I received this product, one of the slats on the door was broken, staples were clearly visible along the side where the slats where attached, and the holes for the knobs that hold up the shelf were drilled unevenly, so the shelf would not sit level. Not worth the price.
